title: Fantastic Four 2 Silver Surfer[2007]Danish/DK[Subtitle]-Freezez
description:
Freezez

This is a Danish subtitle to the movie Fantastic Four 2.

This is not the movie. That you will have to
download beside.

The way you get the subtitle on the movie is to use 
the program GOM Player ore VLC. If you use GOM player

to the screen where the movie is playing. If you use
VLC you shall mount the file when you open the movie.
